title: The rhythm and rhyme of memory, solitude and community | Rosanne Cash
itunes:author: Rosanne Cash
description: "Music can unlock a frozen memory that melts into the seeds of our creativity," says musician Rosanne Cash. Reflecting on the power of memory, solitude and community, she performs "The Sunken Lands" and "Particle And Wave" and meditates on some of life's most poignant and bittersweet themes.
